208    public function writeSpreadsheet(PhpPresentation $presentation, Chart $chart, string $tempName): string
209    {
210        // Need output?
211        if (!$chart->hasIncludedSpreadsheet()) {
212            throw new \Exception('No spreadsheet output is required for the given chart.');
213        }
214
215        // Verify PHPExcel
216        if (!class_exists('PHPExcel')) {
217            throw new \Exception('PHPExcel has not been loaded. Include PHPExcel.php in your script, e.g. require_once \'PHPExcel.php\'.');
218        }
219
220        // Create new spreadsheet
221        $workbook = new \PHPExcel();
222
223        // Set properties
224        $title = $chart->getTitle()->getText();
225        if (0 == strlen($title)) {
226            $title = 'Chart';
227        }
228        $workbook->getProperties()->setCreator($presentation->getDocumentProperties()->getCreator())->setLastModifiedBy($presentation->getDocumentProperties()->getLastModifiedBy())->setTitle($title);
229
230        // Add chart data
231        $sheet = $workbook->setActiveSheetIndex(0);
232        $sheet->setTitle('Sheet1');
233
234        // Write series
235        $seriesIndex = 0;
236        foreach ($chart->getPlotArea()->getType()->getSeries() as $series) {
237            // Title
238            $sheet->setCellValueByColumnAndRow(1 + $seriesIndex, 1, $series->getTitle());
239
240            // X-axis
241            $axisXData = array_keys($series->getValues());
242            $numAxisXData = count($axisXData);
243            for ($i = 0; $i < $numAxisXData; ++$i) {
244                $sheet->setCellValueByColumnAndRow(0, $i + 2, $axisXData[$i]);
245            }
246
247            // Y-axis
248            $axisYData = array_values($series->getValues());
249            $numAxisYData = count($axisYData);
250            for ($i = 0; $i < $numAxisYData; ++$i) {
251                $sheet->setCellValueByColumnAndRow(1 + $seriesIndex, $i + 2, $axisYData[$i]);
252            }
253
254            ++$seriesIndex;
255        }
256
257        // Save to string
258        $writer = \PHPExcel_IOFactory::createWriter($workbook, 'Excel2007');
259        $writer->save($tempName);
260
261        // Load file in memory
262        $returnValue = file_get_contents($tempName);
263        if (false === @unlink($tempName)) {
264            throw new \Exception('The file ' . $tempName . ' could not removed.');
265        }
266
267        return $returnValue;
268    }

466    /**
467     * Write Plot Area.
468     *
469     * @param XMLWriter $objWriter XML Writer
470     *
471     * @throws \Exception
472     */
473    protected function writePlotArea(XMLWriter $objWriter, PlotArea $subject, Chart $chart): void
474    {
475        // c:plotArea
476        $objWriter->startElement('c:plotArea');
477
478        // Write layout
479        $this->writeLayout($objWriter, $subject);
480
481        // Write chart
482        $chartType = $subject->getType();
483        if ($chartType instanceof Area) {
484            $this->writeTypeArea($objWriter, $chartType, $chart->hasIncludedSpreadsheet());
485        } elseif ($chartType instanceof Bar) {
486            $this->writeTypeBar($objWriter, $chartType, $chart->hasIncludedSpreadsheet());
487        } elseif ($chartType instanceof Bar3D) {
488            $this->writeTypeBar3D($objWriter, $chartType, $chart->hasIncludedSpreadsheet());
489        } elseif ($chartType instanceof Doughnut) {
490            $this->writeTypeDoughnut($objWriter, $chartType, $chart->hasIncludedSpreadsheet());
491        } elseif ($chartType instanceof Pie) {
492            $this->writeTypePie($objWriter, $chartType, $chart->hasIncludedSpreadsheet());
493        } elseif ($chartType instanceof Pie3D) {
494            $this->writeTypePie3D($objWriter, $chartType, $chart->hasIncludedSpreadsheet());
495        } elseif ($chartType instanceof Line) {
496            $this->writeTypeLine($objWriter, $chartType, $chart->hasIncludedSpreadsheet());
497        } elseif ($chartType instanceof Scatter) {
498            $this->writeTypeScatter($objWriter, $chartType, $chart->hasIncludedSpreadsheet());
499        } else {
500            throw new \Exception('The chart type provided could not be rendered.');
501        }
502
503        // Write X axis?
504        if ($chartType->hasAxisX()) {
505            $this->writeAxis($objWriter, $subject->getAxisX(), Chart\Axis::AXIS_X, $chartType);
506        }
507
508        // Write Y axis?
509        if ($chartType->hasAxisY()) {
510            $this->writeAxis($objWriter, $subject->getAxisY(), Chart\Axis::AXIS_Y, $chartType);
511        }
512
513        $objWriter->endElement();
514    }

659            $objWriter->endElement();

673    /**

677     * @param Chart\Type\Area $subject
678     *
679     * @throws \Exception

681    protected function writeTypeArea(XMLWriter $objWriter, Area $subject, bool $includeSheet = false): void
682    {

689        $objWriter->endElement();
690
691        // Write series
692        $seriesIndex = 0;
693        foreach ($subject->getSeries() as $series) {
694            // c:ser
695            $objWriter->startElement('c:ser');
696
697            // c:ser > c:idx
698            $objWriter->startElement('c:idx');

700            $objWriter->endElement();
701
702            // c:ser > c:order
703            $objWriter->startElement('c:order');
704            $objWriter->writeAttribute('val', $seriesIndex);

706

708            $objWriter->startElement('c:tx');
709            $coords = ($includeSheet ? 'Sheet1!$' . \PHPExcel_Cell::stringFromColumnIndex(1 + $seriesIndex) . '$1' : '');
710            $this->writeSingleValueOrReference($objWriter, $includeSheet, $series->getTitle(), $coords);
711            $objWriter->endElement();
712
713            // c:ser > c:dLbls
714            // @link : https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/documentformat.openxml.drawing.charts.areachartseries.aspx

716

718            $this->writeElementWithValAttribute($objWriter, 'c:showVal', $series->hasShowValue() ? '1' : '0');
719
720            // c:ser > c:dLbls > c:showCatName
721            $this->writeElementWithValAttribute($objWriter, 'c:showCatName', $series->hasShowCategoryName() ? '1' : '0');
722
723            // c:ser > c:dLbls > c:showSerName
724            $this->writeElementWithValAttribute($objWriter, 'c:showSerName', $series->hasShowSeriesName() ? '1' : '0');
725
726            // c:ser > c:dLbls > c:showPercent
727            $this->writeElementWithValAttribute($objWriter, 'c:showPercent', $series->hasShowPercentage() ? '1' : '0');
728
729            // c:ser > ##c:dLbls
730            $objWriter->endElement();
731
732            if (Fill::FILL_NONE != $series->getFill()->getFillType()) {
733                // c:spPr
734                $objWriter->startElement('c:spPr');
735                // Write fill
736                $this->writeFill($objWriter, $series->getFill());
737                // ## c:spPr
738                $objWriter->endElement();
739            }
740
741            // Write X axis data
742            $axisXData = array_keys($series->getValues());
743
744            // c:cat
745            $objWriter->startElement('c:cat');
746            $this->writeMultipleValuesOrReference($objWriter, $includeSheet, $axisXData, 'Sheet1!$A$2:$A$' . (1 + count($axisXData)));
747            $objWriter->endElement();
748
749            // Write Y axis data
750            $axisYData = array_values($series->getValues());
751
752            // c:val
753            $objWriter->startElement('c:val');
754            $coords = ($includeSheet ? 'Sheet1!$' . \PHPExcel_Cell::stringFromColumnIndex($seriesIndex + 1) . '$2:$' . \PHPExcel_Cell::stringFromColumnIndex($seriesIndex + 1) . '$' . (1 + count($axisYData)) : '');
755            $this->writeMultipleValuesOrReference($objWriter, $includeSheet, $axisYData, $coords);
756            $objWriter->endElement();
757
758            $objWriter->endElement();
759
760            ++$seriesIndex;
761        }
762
763        // c:axId
764        $objWriter->startElement('c:axId');
765        $objWriter->writeAttribute('val', '52743552');
766        $objWriter->endElement();
767
768        // c:axId
769        $objWriter->startElement('c:axId');
770        $objWriter->writeAttribute('val', '52749440');
771        $objWriter->endElement();
772
773        $objWriter->endElement();
774    }
